    "en": {
      "title": "The news about Brigadier is false",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Brigadier Anil Somaweera, who was in service during the demonstration in front of the Prime Minister's office on the 13th, has been dismissed, said Brigadier Nilantha Premaratne, the spokesperson of the military media, that the news published on social media is untrue.",
        "The spokesperson also pointed out that the officer in question is attached to Army Headquarters for other duties.",
        "This announcement came at a time when Lakshman Kiriella, a Member of Parliament of the United People's Shakti, had mentioned that the news about the dismissal of the Brigadier had been published in a media conference."
      ],
